# Walkthrough — WinNative UI Overhaul

## What Was Done

### 1. Menu Cleanup (MainActivity / Navigation Drawer)

Removed Winlator branding, Toolbar, and reorganized the navigation drawer:
- **Stores, Presets, Components, Drivers, Input Controls** (visible)
- **Containers, About** (hidden, used for internal navigation)

**Files changed:**
- [main_menu.xml](file:///home/max/Build/Emulator/WinNative/app/src/main/res/menu/main_menu.xml)
- [main_activity.xml](file:///home/max/Build/Emulator/WinNative/app/src/main/res/layout/main_activity.xml)
- [containers_fragment.xml](file:///home/max/Build/Emulator/WinNative/app/src/main/res/layout/containers_fragment.xml)
- [strings.xml](file:///home/max/Build/Emulator/WinNative/app/src/main/res/values/strings.xml)

---

### 2. UnifiedActivity Redesign

Complete rewrite of [UnifiedActivity.kt](file:///home/max/Build/Emulator/WinNative/app/src/main/java/com/winlator/cmod/UnifiedActivity.kt):

| Feature | Implementation |
|---|---|
| **PS5-style carousel** | `LazyRow` with `derivedStateOf` center detection, animated scale (1.12x center / 0.88x others), accent glow shadow |
| **Adaptive tabs** | AIO mode: Library/Downloads/Store; Non-AIO: Library/Downloads/Steam/Epic/GOG/Amazon |
| **Shadow pill header** | `RoundedCornerShape(24.dp)` with `shadow(8.dp)`, `horizontalScroll` for overflow |
| **Button shadows** | Circle shadows on Settings, Controller, and Profile buttons |
| **Steam status** | Circular avatar with `DropdownMenu` for Online/Away/Invisible via `SteamService.setPersonaState()` |
| **Artwork fix** | Prioritize [getHeaderImageUrl()](file:///home/max/Build/Emulator/WinNative/app/src/main/java/com/winlator/cmod/steam/data/SteamApp.kt#164-169) → [getCapsuleUrl()](file:///home/max/Build/Emulator/WinNative/app/src/main/java/com/winlator/cmod/steam/data/SteamApp.kt#170-181) → CDN fallback, with `crossfade(300)` |
| **Store placeholders** | Epic/GOG/Amazon placeholder tabs with Sign In buttons |

---

### 3. Filter Panel

Bottom-left filter icon opens an animated slide-up panel:
- **AIO Store Mode** toggle (persisted to `PrefManager.aioStoreMode`)
- **Store toggles**: Steam, Epic, GOG, Amazon — hides tabs (non-AIO) or filters games (AIO)
- **Content type toggles**: Games (on by default), DLC, Applications, Tools

---

### 4. New Utilities & Preferences

- [StringUtils.kt](file:///home/max/Build/Emulator/WinNative/app/src/main/java/com/winlator/cmod/steam/utils/StringUtils.kt) — `String.getAvatarURL()` extension
- [PrefManager.kt](file:///home/max/Build/Emulator/WinNative/app/src/main/java/com/winlator/cmod/steam/utils/PrefManager.kt) — Added `aioStoreMode` boolean

---

### 5. Application Icon

Replaced [ic_launcher_foreground.xml](file:///home/max/Build/Emulator/WinNative/app/src/main/res/drawable/ic_launcher_foreground.xml) with a gradient blue rounded box containing a stylized "W" stroke.

